    "body": "> What is the motivation of not throwing an error?\n\n@Jerskouille answered but yes the most common case would be that as a developer I would change my mind and switch from 20 to 30 hits per page by default in my hits widget. Then my previous urls with hPP in it would trigger a throw, not good\n",
